WHICH WAS WORSE IS BACK! The series that has The Don and Dan The Comic Man defending the indefensible returns with a rare wrinkle. In this episode, the guys pit 2010's Jonah Hex against 1986's Howard The Duck! Thing is, neither Dan nor The Don has seen EITHER film until this moment! What film will be crown definitively worse? You decide as you listen to another banger episode of the Major Issues Podcast!

